org.obrel.space

Interface ObjectSpaceResolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryFunction<Relatable,RelationType<?>,java.lang.Object>, java.util.function.Function<Relatable,java.lang.Object>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ObjectSpaceResolver.DeleteResolver, ObjectSpaceResolver.GetResolver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectSpaceResolver.PutResolver

    public interface ObjectSpaceResolver
extends BinaryFunction<Relatable,RelationType<?>,java.lang.Object>
    A binary function extension that resolves URLs in object spaces. Invoked by ObjectRelations.urlResolve(Relatable, String, boolean, ObjectSpaceResolver).

    • Method Detail

      • resolve

        java.lang.Object resolve(ObjectSpace<?> rSpace,
                         java.lang.String sRelativeUrl)
        Resolves a URL in a certain ObjectSpace. Will be invoked by ObjectRelations.urlResolve(Relatable, String, boolean, ObjectSpaceResolver) for the remaining URL if the URL traversal encounters an object space element.
        Parameters:
        rSpace - The object space to resolve the URL in
        sRelativeUrl - The space-relative URL to resolve
        Returns:
        The resolved object (NULL for none)
